item.title: CVE-2023-6623|2024-01-15T15:10:40.328Z -- unknown -- essential%20blocks
item.description: The Essential Blocks WordPress plugin before 4.4.3 does not prevent unauthenticated attackers from overwriting local variables when rendering templates over the REST API, which may lead to Local File Inclusion attacks.
